Name: The Sopranos
Title: Cold Stones
Desc: A.J.'s apathy angers Tony; Carmela travels to Paris with Rosalie; Vito returns to New Jersey.
LongDescription: Carmela begins to rethink her life after she goes out for a day with Rosalie. Meadow decides it's time to find a new place to live. Tony and the gang suddenly find themselves in a place they have never been before -- lacking funds.
